-- Egypt Won't Allow Short Selling Before Stock Market Recovers, Borsa Says
-- Alaa Shahine
-- 2010-06-20T07:07:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-20/egypt-won-t-allow-short-selling-before-stock-market-recovers-borsa-says.html

          
          
             Egypt’s financial markets regulator
won’t allow short selling before the stock market of the Arab
country recovers, Al Borsa newspaper reported, citing Ziad Bahaa
El-Din, chairman of the regulatory authority.  
